# Upload filter for `vercel deploy`. This file exists because `data/*.sqlite` is
# git-ignored (the DB is a derived, disposable projection and must stay out of git),
# but it MUST be uploaded so `vercel.json`'s functions.includeFiles can bundle it.
# Without a .vercelignore the CLI falls back to .gitignore and the DB never arrives,
# and every endpoint fails with `db_not_found`.
node_modules/
.vercel/
dist/
